---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="legal-wrap">
      <header class="legal-header">
        <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
        <h1 class="text-section-heading">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </header>

      <div class="legal-body">
        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p>
            Aurea Development Group ("we", "us", "our") operates this website at <strong
              >aurearresidences.com</strong
            > (the "Site"). We are committed to protecting your personal data and handling it with the
            care and discretion you would expect.
          </p>
          <p>
            For privacy-related enquiries, contact us at <a
              href="mailto:privacy@aurearresidences.com">privacy@aurearresidences.com</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>2. What Data We Collect</h2>
          <p>We may collect the following categories of personal data:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Contact information</strong> — name, email address, phone number, when submitted
              via enquiry or viewing request forms.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time on site, browser type, device type, and
              IP address, collected automatically via analytics tools.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Cookie data</strong> — identifiers stored in your browser as described in Section
              5 below.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Communication records</strong> — any correspondence you send us, including enquiry
              details and preferences.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <p>We use your personal data to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Respond to enquiries and schedule viewings</li>
            <li>
              Keep you informed of availability, pricing, and development updates (where you have
              consented)
            </li>
            <li>Improve the Site and our marketing through anonymised analytics</li>
            <li>Comply with legal and regulatory obligations</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We will never sell your personal data to third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
          <p>We process your data on the following legal bases:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Consent</strong> — where you have opted in to marketing communications or cookie
              use.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Legitimate interests</strong> — to respond to enquiries and improve our services,
              where this does not override your rights.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Legal obligation</strong> — where required by applicable law.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            This Site uses cookies — small text files stored in your browser — to improve your
            experience and analyse how the Site is used. The types of cookies we use include:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Essential cookies</strong> — required for the Site to function correctly. These
              cannot be disabled.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Analytics cookies</strong> — help us understand how visitors interact with the Site
              (e.g. Google Analytics). Data is aggregated and anonymised where possible.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Marketing cookies</strong> — used to deliver relevant content and measure the effectiveness
              of campaigns, only where you have consented.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings. Withdrawing consent for
            non-essential cookies will not affect your ability to browse the Site.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>6. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We may share your data with trusted third parties who support the operation of this Site
            and our sales process, including:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>CRM and email marketing platforms (e.g. HubSpot, Mailchimp)</li>
            <li>Analytics providers (e.g. Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>Sales agents and representatives acting on our behalf</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            All third parties are contractually required to handle your data securely and only for
            the purposes we specify.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            We retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes outlined in
            this Policy, or as required by law. Enquiry data is typically retained for up to 3 years
            after your last interaction with us. You may request deletion at any time (see Section
            9).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>8. International Transfers</h2>
          <p>
            Some of our third-party service providers operate outside your country of residence.
            Where personal data is transferred internationally, we ensure appropriate safeguards are
            in place in accordance with applicable data protection law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>9. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data ("right to be forgotten")</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time (without affecting prior processing)</li>
            <li>Lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a
              href="mailto:privacy@aurearresidences.com">privacy@aurearresidences.com</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>10. Security</h2>
          <p>
            We take reasonable technical and organisational measures to protect your personal data
            against unauthorised access, loss, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission
            over the internet is entirely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be noted with
            a revised "Last updated" date at the top of this page. Continued use of the Site after
            changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="legal-section">
          <h2>12. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your data, please contact
            us at <a href="mailto:privacy@aurearresidences.com">privacy@aurearresidences.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="link-underline legal-back">Return home</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-wrap {
    max-width: 48rem;
    padding: 0 var(--space-edge);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-top: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem);
  }

  .legal-header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 4rem);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-meta {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-black) 40%, transparent);
  }

  .legal-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--color-black);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-section p,
  .legal-section li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-body);
    line-height: var(--leading-body);
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-black) 65%, transparent);
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .legal-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-black);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .legal-back {
    display: inline-block;
  }
</style>
